		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think I'll stick with .ips format, but I'll be glad to provide a CRC16 checksum for all my games. I'll try to upload them to the forum but I think there's a 2MB limit on files. Some of my files such as my FDS hacks need to stay on Mediafire for that reason. <br /><br />Okay. I'll give one for this game:<br /><br />Original, unhacked version: CRC16 = DE2A<br />In its hacked .nes file format: CRC16 = DDEA <br /><br />This hack was completed by myself on 12/13/13. I'll add them to my other games, tomorrow. Thanks. That's a good idea for file integrity. ^_^

		

