	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Okay. I've made 2 fixes.<br /><br />1) Made it so that the player starts off with five lives, just like in the SNES Allstars version. ($04ED appears to be the lives counter. I traced code and found an LDA #$03 STA $04ED. ROM location is 0x1E425)<br /><br />2) Made the game to have five continues, instead of two. (Counter for this is found at RAM $05C5)<br /><br />SMB USA original ROM CRC16 = DE2A<br /><br />--<em><strong>ShaneM</strong></em><br /><br />SEE BELOW FOR FINAL DOWNLOAD

		

		</td>
